		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Ranger/Mage Duo<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Ranger/Mage Duo";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Mon, Mar 28th 12:18 AM2005 </span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/forum.html?forum=1&mid=111198705221414760&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/forum.html?forum=1&mid=111198705221414760&num=2&post=1&replyto=111198705221414760"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=111198705221414760></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=249628"><span id="">baileyzen</span></a><b><span id=""></span></b><br />6 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=baileyzen&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>I just got a 2nd computer. I am moving my level 61 Magician with 5 AAs to a seperate account so I can play her and my 62 Ranger with 140 AAs together. I have searched the boards and have not found any advice or examples of playing these two characters together. I am looking for some suggestions and hunting spots. My initial intention is to get the Mage her DPoC (halfway there) and SCM 3 before levelling hardcore to 66 for the better Air pet. The Ranger I would like to keep 62 until she has saved 30 AA for Fero 2/3, FoTA 2/3, ID 3/4/5, LR 3/4/5 on the way to 65, keeping those AA sets maxed along the way. <br /> <br />The Ranger has all offensive AAs possible at 62 and almost all defensive ones, she's been Headshot farming AAs for many months in hopes of a substantial upgrade with the class re-envisioning. Both character have about the best bazaar gear possible at their level. <br /> <br />Any suggestions, help and advice would be appreciated, please no, &quot;Ranger Down&quot;, remarks, I've heard 'em all... <br /> <br />Baileyzen</p>
</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >2 Replies</td></tr></table>
